---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
const title = "BSc Nursing Abroad 2026 | No NEET | Top Countries | Gradiks";
const description = "BSc Nursing abroad for Indian students. Georgia, Albania, Bulgaria, Malta, UK. No NEET required. English medium. Admissions open for 2026 batch. Get free cost breakdown.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
<Navigation />

<main>
<!-- TRUST TICKER — auto-scrolling marquee -->
<div class="trust-bar" style="overflow: hidden;">
  <div class="trust-ticker-track" aria-label="Key statistics">
    <span class="trust-stat">350+ students</span>
    <span class="trust-label">placed across 5 countries</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat">100% visa</span>
    <span class="trust-label">success rate</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat accent">₹80K/mo</span>
    <span class="trust-label">avg starting salary abroad</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat">24hr</span>
    <span class="trust-label">response guaranteed</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->
    <span class="trust-stat">350+ students</span>
    <span class="trust-label">placed across 5 countries</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat">100% visa</span>
    <span class="trust-label">success rate</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat accent">₹80K/mo</span>
    <span class="trust-label">avg starting salary abroad</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
    <span class="trust-stat">24hr</span>
    <span class="trust-label">response guaranteed</span>
    <span class="trust-divider" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HERO — Salary-led headline -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <!-- Student visa proof strip — mobile -->
    <div class="hero-faces lg:hidden">
      <div class="hero-faces-row">
        <img src="/students/visa-student-1.jpeg" alt="" class="hero-face-card" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-4.jpeg" alt="" class="hero-face-card" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-5.jpeg" alt="" class="hero-face-card" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-7.jpeg" alt="" class="hero-face-card" />
      </div>
      <span class="hero-faces-label">Visas approved this week 🇬🇪</span>
    </div>
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">BSc Nursing Abroad — 2026 Batch Open</p>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">
      Your Child Deserves<br>
      <span class="hero-headline-accent">₹80K/Month.</span><br>
      <span class="hero-subtitle">Not ₹12K.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-subheadline">
      BSc Nursing abroad. Same 4-year degree. NMC recognized.
      5 countries. No NEET. English medium. 5–8x the salary.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <button onclick="document.getElementById('lead-form-container')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' })" class="cta-primary hidden lg:inline-flex">
        Get free cost breakdown
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="lg:hidden w-full mt-2">
        <form id="hero-lead-form" class="space-y-3">
          <input type="text" name="name" required class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name *" aria-label="Full Name" autocomplete="name">
          <input type="tel" name="phone" required class="form-input" placeholder="Your phone number *" aria-label="Phone Number" autocomplete="tel">
          <input type="email" name="email" required class="form-input" placeholder="Email *" aria-label="Email Address" autocomplete="email">
          <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-[#be1e2d] text-white font-semibold tracking-wide text-sm flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            GET FREE COST BREAKDOWN
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </button>
          <p class="text-center text-[10px] text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Free · No spam · 24hr response</p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta">
      <span>NMC recognized</span>
      <span class="meta-dot" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span>No NEET required</span>
      <span class="meta-dot" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span>English medium</span>
      <span class="meta-dot" aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span>5 countries</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Curiosity hook — scroll to visa gallery -->
    <button onclick="document.getElementById('visa-gallery')?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'center' })" class="visa-teaser" aria-label="See recent visa approvals">
      <div class="visa-teaser-faces">
        <img src="/students/visa-student-1.jpeg" alt="" class="visa-teaser-face" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-4.jpeg" alt="" class="visa-teaser-face" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-5.jpeg" alt="" class="visa-teaser-face" />
        <img src="/students/visa-student-7.jpeg" alt="" class="visa-teaser-face" />
        <span class="visa-teaser-more">+8</span>
      </div>
      <div class="visa-teaser-text">
        <span class="visa-teaser-count">12 visas approved</span>
        <span class="visa-teaser-cta">this month — see proof ↓</span>
      </div>
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
    <div class="hero-collage">
      <img src="/students/visa-student-1.jpeg" alt="Alvin Jijo — Visa approved for BSc Nursing, Georgia" class="hero-collage-img hero-collage-main" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
      <img src="/students/visa-student-4.jpeg" alt="Student visa approved" class="hero-collage-img hero-collage-sm-1" loading="eager" />
      <img src="/students/visa-student-5.jpeg" alt="Student visa approved" class="hero-collage-img hero-collage-sm-2" loading="eager" />
      <img src="/students/visa-student-7.jpeg" alt="Student visa approved" class="hero-collage-img hero-collage-sm-3" loading="eager" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-collage-label">
      <span class="hero-badge">12 visas this month</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-country-flags">🇬🇪 🇦🇱 🇧🇬 🇲🇹 🇬🇧</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SALARY COMPARISON — The anchor moment -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-8 px-6">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mb-3">The Real Difference</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">Same Degree.<br><span class="section-headline-muted">Different Life.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="salary-comparison">
      <div>
        <div class="salary-big muted">₹12K/mo</div>
        <div class="salary-label">Fresh BSc Nurse in India</div>
      </div>
      <div class="salary-divider">vs</div>
      <div>
        <div class="salary-big accent">₹80K–₹2L/mo</div>
        <div class="salary-label">Same degree, working abroad</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center text-sm text-[#6b7280] mt-8 px-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">Same 4-year NMC-recognized BSc Nursing. Same qualification. The only difference is where you study — and that changes everything.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DESTINATIONS — Featured + Compact -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#f9fafb] border-y border-[#e5e7eb]">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto">
    <div class="section-header" style="padding-bottom: 2rem;">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">5 Destinations</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">Study Nursing<br><span class="section-headline-muted">in Your Budget</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc">From ₹4L/year to ₹20L+ — a country for every mark sheet and bank balance.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Featured: Georgia (cheapest) + UK (highest ROI) -->
    <div class="destination-featured">
      <div class="country-card">
        <div class="country-image-wrap">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565008576549-57569a49371d?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Tbilisi, Georgia" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="country-overlay">
            <span class="country-flag">🇬🇪</span>
            <span class="country-tag">Most Affordable</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="country-body">
          <h3 class="country-name">Georgia</h3>
          <p class="country-desc">European BSc Nursing at Asian cost. Any stream can apply. No IELTS. 50% and above eligible.</p>
          <div class="country-stats">
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">4 Years</span><span class="stat-key">Duration</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">₹2.5–4.5L</span><span class="stat-key">Tuition/yr</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">₹1–1.5L</span><span class="stat-key">Living/yr</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat accent"><span class="stat-val">₹1–1.5L</span><span class="stat-key">Salary/mo after</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-intakes">50% min · No IELTS · Intakes: Feb &amp; Sep</div>
          <a href="/nursing-georgia" class="cta-primary mt-4 w-full justify-center text-sm py-3">Explore Georgia →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="country-card">
        <div class="country-image-wrap">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513635269975-59663e0ac1ad?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="London, United Kingdom" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="country-overlay">
            <span class="country-flag">🇬🇧</span>
            <span class="country-tag">Highest ROI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="country-body">
          <h3 class="country-name">United Kingdom</h3>
          <p class="country-desc">BSc Nursing (Hons) at UK universities. Work 20 hrs/week. Post-study work visa. 60% and above eligible.</p>
          <div class="country-stats">
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">3 Years</span><span class="stat-key">Duration</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">₹12–18L</span><span class="stat-key">Tuition/yr</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat"><span class="stat-val">₹8–12L</span><span class="stat-key">Living/yr</span></div>
            <div class="country-stat accent"><span class="stat-val">₹2.2–3L</span><span class="stat-key">Salary/mo after</span></div>
          </div>
          <div class="country-intakes">60% min · IELTS 6.0+ · Work Rights: ✓</div>
          <a href="/nursing-uk" class="cta-primary mt-4 w-full justify-center text-sm py-3">Explore UK →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Compact: Albania, Bulgaria, Malta — with entry requirements -->
    <div class="destination-compact">
      <a href="/nursing-albania" class="country-row" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <span class="country-row-flag">🇦🇱</span>
        <span class="country-row-name">Albania</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat"><strong>₹3–5L</strong>/yr · 65% min · No IELTS</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat">4 Years</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat" style="color: var(--color-gold-500);"><strong>₹85K–1.25L</strong>/mo →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/nursing-bulgaria" class="country-row" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <span class="country-row-flag">🇧🇬</span>
        <span class="country-row-name">Bulgaria</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat"><strong>₹3.5–6L</strong>/yr · 62% min · No IELTS</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat">4 Years</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat" style="color: var(--color-gold-500);"><strong>₹1.25–1.9L</strong>/mo →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/nursing-malta" class="country-row" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <span class="country-row-flag">🇲🇹</span>
        <span class="country-row-name">Malta</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat"><strong>₹7–10L</strong>/yr · English speaking</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat">3–4 Years</span>
        <span class="country-row-stat" style="color: var(--color-gold-500);"><strong>₹1.25–2.1L</strong>/mo →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Entry requirements summary -->
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 mt-8">
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        <strong class="text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Any stream can apply</strong> — not just PCB. No IELTS required for Georgia, Albania, and Bulgaria.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INDIA vs ABROAD — Fees Comparison -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mb-3">Fees in INR</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">India vs Abroad<br><span class="section-headline-muted">Real Cost Comparison</span></h2>
      <p class="section-desc mx-auto">Parents ask: "Isn't abroad expensive?" Here are the actual numbers — including what you'd really pay in India.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- India costs -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          🇮🇳 BSc Nursing in India
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Kerala — Govt college tuition (4 yrs)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹1,06,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Kerala — Donation / capitation</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-500)]">₹8–12 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Food &amp; accommodation (4 yrs)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹3–4 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Karnataka / TN — Medical college (pvt)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹12–16 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">Karnataka / TN — Normal college (pvt)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹8–11 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 bg-[var(--color-surface)] px-3 -mx-3">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Realistic total (Kerala private)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">₹12–17 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Salary after graduation</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">₹8–15K/month</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Abroad costs -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
          🌍 BSc Nursing Abroad
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">🇬🇪 Georgia — Total 4 years</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹14–24 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">🇦🇱 Albania — Total 4 years</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹16–26 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">🇧🇬 Bulgaria — Total 4 years</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹19–31 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">🇲🇹 Malta — Total 4 years</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹34–48 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">🇬🇧 UK — Total 3 years</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">₹60–90 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-3 bg-[oklch(0.95_0.02_25)] px-3 -mx-3">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Georgia (most affordable)</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-gold-500)]">₹14–24 lakhs</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center py-2">
            <span class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Salary after graduation</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-[var(--color-gold-500)]">₹80K–₹2L/month</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center mt-10 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)] max-w-lg mx-auto" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">
      Georgia costs roughly the same as Kerala private nursing — but the salary after graduation is 8–10x higher.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY THIS WORKS — 3 zones -->
<section class="why-section">
  <div class="why-header">
    <p class="section-eyebrow inverted">Why This Works</p>
    <h2 class="section-headline inverted">The Two Things<br>Parents Ask First</h2>
  </div>

  <!-- Zone A: Deal-breakers -->
  <div class="why-dealbreakers">
    <div class="dealbreaker-card">
      <div class="dealbreaker-badge">✓ Confirmed</div>
      <h3 class="dealbreaker-title">No NEET · No IELTS · Any Stream</h3>
      <p class="dealbreaker-desc">Unlike MBBS, BSc Nursing abroad doesn't need NEET or IELTS (except UK). Any 12th stream can apply — not just PCB. Georgia accepts 50%+, UK accepts 60%+, Albania 65%+. Your child's marks are enough.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="dealbreaker-card">
      <div class="dealbreaker-badge">✓ Confirmed</div>
      <h3 class="dealbreaker-title">NMC Recognized — Valid in India</h3>
      <p class="dealbreaker-desc">Every university we recommend is NMC recognized. Your child can return to India, pass the screening test, register with the State Nursing Council, and practice in any government or private hospital.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Zone B: Advantages -->
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="why-title">English Medium Only</h3>
      <p class="why-desc">Every program is fully English-taught. No foreign language requirement. Indian students adapt faster, academically and socially.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="why-title">Work While Studying</h3>
      <p class="why-desc">UK allows 20 hrs/week part-time. Georgia, Albania, and Bulgaria offer on-campus work. Offset living costs while building your career network.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="why-title">International Salary</h3>
      <p class="why-desc">UK nurses earn £25–35K/year. Malta and Bulgaria nurses earn €18–28K/year. Gulf countries offer tax-free salaries. Same degree, 5x the pay.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Zone C: Editorial truth -->
  <div class="why-editorial">
    <p class="why-editorial-text">
      In India, nurses are overworked and earn ₹8–15K/month. Abroad, they're <strong>valued professionals</strong>. Same qualification. Completely different life. The BSc Nursing abroad route exists because <strong>India failed to fix this</strong>. Don't wait for it to change.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STUDENT STORIES — Asymmetric -->
<section class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-[#f9fafb]">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 px-6">
      <p class="section-eyebrow mb-3">Real Students. Real Salaries.</p>
      <h2 class="section-headline">They Were Where<br><span class="section-headline-muted">Your Child Is Now</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="stories-grid">
      <!-- Featured testimonial -->
      <div class="testimonial-card--featured">
        <div class="testimonial-person">
          <div class="person-avatar">R</div>
          <div class="person-info">
            <div class="person-name">Rahul <span class="person-loc">🇮🇳 Kerala</span></div>
            <div class="person-detail">BSc Nursing · European University, Tirana, Albania · 2024 batch</div>
          </div>
        </div>
